-.05-.06-.06-.09a.12.12 0 010-.07c0-.02.02-.04.06-.08l57.7-57.69c.03-.04.05-.05.07-.06a.12.12 0 01.07 0c.03 0 .05.02.09.06L512 454.07l287.7-287.7c.04-.04.06-.05.09-.06a.12.12 0 01.07 0z"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messagesContainer__yLSny"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_message__KoyES PromptMasterDrawer_userMessage__9IacO"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageAvatar__T0gzC"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_userAvatar__cKbPR">👤</div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_avatarName__1tjpv">用户</div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageContent__OV62A"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageHeader__5sjet"><div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageImages__mFHRC"><img src="https://eva-1313581156.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/Eva%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/eva_imgs/gemini_demo_0.png?imageMogr2/quality/100/format/webp/interlace/0/thumbnail/200x" alt="示例图片 1" class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageImage__swIPc"/></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_bubble__KjbV_ PromptMasterDrawer_bubbleUser__6NlFT"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageText__hRCA6"><span class="PromptMasterDrawer_promptPrefix__gyNtf">大白话：</span>帮我把这个图片变得好看一点</div></div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_message__KoyES PromptMasterDrawer_aiMessage__VKXJn"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageAvatar__T0gzC"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_aiAvatar__i4EgQ"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:20px;height:20px"><path d="M12 2L14.85 8.15L21 11L14.85 13.85L12 20L9.15 13.85L3 11L9.15 8.15L12 2Z" fill="white" style="filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.8))"></path></svg></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_avatarName__1tjpv">谷歌Gemini</div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageContent__OV62A"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageHeader__5sjet"><div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_bubble__KjbV_ PromptMasterDrawer_bubbleAi__jrhgt"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageText__hRCA6"><span class="PromptMasterDrawer_promptPrefix__gyNtf">专业话术：</span>保留现有卧室的整体构图与布局，将背景大理石墙面更换为具有细腻天然纹理的深灰色爵士白大理石，并嵌入哑光黄铜拉丝金属线条。床品升级为高支数丝滑棉质面料，呈现自然的褶皱感与厚实感，枕头增加深蓝色丝绒与浅灰色亚麻的多层叠放。地面人字拼木地板纹理需更清晰，展现温润的木质光泽。整体画质提升至8K超高清，强化大理石、金属、布料与木材的材质区分度，营造一种极简轻奢、宁静优雅的现代室内摄影质感。</div></div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_message__KoyES PromptMasterDrawer_userMessage__9IacO"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageAvatar__T0gzC"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_userAvatar__cKbPR">👤</div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_avatarName__1tjpv">用户</div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageContent__OV62A"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageHeader__5sjet"><div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageImages__mFHRC"><img src="https://eva-1313581156.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/Eva%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/eva_imgs/gemini_demo_1.webp?imageMogr2/quality/100/format/webp/interlace/0/thumbnail/200x" alt="示例图片 1" class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageImage__swIPc"/><img src="https://eva-1313581156.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/Eva%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/eva_imgs/gemini_demo_2.webp?imageMogr2/quality/100/format/webp/interlace/0/thumbnail/200x" alt="示例图片 2" class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageImage__swIPc"/></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_bubble__KjbV_ PromptMasterDrawer_bubbleUser__6NlFT"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageText__hRCA6"><span class="PromptMasterDrawer_promptPrefix__gyNtf">大白话：</span>我想把图片1变成图片2的那种展现形式</div></div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_message__KoyES PromptMasterDrawer_aiMessage__VKXJn"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageAvatar__T0gzC"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_aiAvatar__i4EgQ"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:20px;height:20px"><path d="M12 2L14.85 8.15L21 11L14.85 13.85L12 20L9.15 13.85L3 11L9.15 8.15L12 2Z" fill="white" style="filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.8))"></path></svg></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_avatarName__1tjpv">谷歌Gemini</div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageContent__OV62A"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageHeader__5sjet"><div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_bubble__KjbV_ PromptMasterDrawer_bubbleAi__jrhgt"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_messageText__hRCA6"><span class="PromptMasterDrawer_promptPrefix__gyNtf">专业话术：</span>保持原建筑的几何构图与主体轮廓不变，将画面渲染为高端现代中式建筑风格。建筑材质升级为精致的深灰色大理石、浅灰色石材面板与深棕色金属格栅。增强光影效果，在檐口、台阶及建筑内侧加入暖色调线性藏灯与射灯，营造出如黄昏时分华灯初上的温馨与尊贵感。背景天空替换为纯净的蓝调暮色，地面材质改为平整的高级石材铺装。整体画面追求极致的真实感、光泽质感与高级写意的建筑氛围。</div></div></div></div><div></div></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_inputArea__ovhPG"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_inputWrapper__etKN6"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_textareaRow___prv7"><span class="PromptMasterDrawer_textareaPrefix__vn8kz" aria-hidden="true">大白话：</span><textarea class="PromptMasterDrawer_textareaInput__fEWVr" placeholder="用大白话说你的要求，可直接发文字，也可配图..." rows="3"></textarea></div><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_inputFooter__ESXiM"><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_footerLeft__gKKsE"><span class="ant-upload-wrapper css-198drv2"><div class="ant-upload ant-upload-select"><span class="ant-upload"><input type="file" style="display:none" accept="image/*" name="file"/><div class="PromptMasterDrawer_iconBtn__hq_q7 " title="上传图片"><span role="img" aria-label="plus" class="anticon anticon-plus"><svg viewBox="64 64 896 896" focusable="false" data-icon="plus" width="1em" height="1em" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M482 152h60q8 0 8 8v704q0 8-8 8h-60q-8 0-8-8V160q0-8 8-8z"></path><path d="M192 474h672q8 0 8 8v60q0 8-8 8H160q-8 0-8-8v-60q0-8 8-8z"></path></svg></span></div></span></div></span></div><span style="display:inline-flex" aria-describedby=":R1arldtb:"><button class="PromptMasterDrawer_sendButton__MfM6d" disabled=""><span role="img" aria-label="send" style="position:relative;top:-2px;left:2px;transform:rotate(-45deg)" class="anticon anticon-send"><svg viewBox="64 64 896 896" focusable="false" data-icon="send" width="1em" height="1em" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><defs><style></style></defs><path d="M931.